Combat in this game works without any brain power with swinging the golf club hitting enemies, it all contains hitting the animals whilst avoiding their attacks and working on your next move. There is a clear delay between hitting the attack button and swinging occurring so you need to get used to timing to succeed within this game. One can also improve themselves in this game as well by buying better golf clubs although enough credit for that to occur is hard to get. A highlight here is Boss Battles with combat although a player needs to go 1/2 way through the game to be able to do this.  
 
