Things to improve within’ this game include how it visually looks, whilst it looks good, to compare it to other indie games it does not deliver at all with a similar scenario occurring for the sound effects and music in the background with them being serviceable but not legendary in any shape nor form.  
 
Whilst this is a much better sequel, RPGolf legends does not have anything to makes it an iconic and unique game to play in the market with the game not feeling fulfilling. 
 

